[Radiation induced brachial plexopathy: Diagnosis, risk factors, principles of 
care].

[Article in French]

Miran C(1), Bonnet E(2), Lafont C(3), Baseilhac P(4), Clippe S(2), El Hedi Zouai 
M(2), Langrand-Escure J(2), Bosset M(2), Fleury B(2), Guy JB(5).

